tf3of3m98QalXA">Hí vi lục tuyệt cú kỳ 1 - 戲為六絕句其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BB%93ng/Ho%C3%A1n-kh%C3%AA-sa-Mai-Tinh-s%C6%A1n-ng%E1%BB%99-tuy%E1%BA%BFt/poem-MfcNoYhaLU-TwR3tEZaWUA">Hoán khê sa - Mai Tinh sơn ngộ tuyết - 浣溪沙－梅菁山遇雪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-scROveDf2WzzNJM9eAvSlQ">Lý Hồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ki%E1%BB%81u-L%C4%83ng-thi-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn-nh%C3%A2n-tr%C3%ACnh-huy%E1%BB%87n-n%E1%BB%99i-ch%C6%B0-quan/poem-iMd00tDBdT14eExlDSnUyw">Kiều Lăng thi tam thập vận, nhân trình huyện nội chư quan - 橋陵詩三十韻，因呈縣內諸官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/L%E1%BA%ABm-l%E1%BA%ABm-tu%E1%BA%BF-v%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99/poem-T_b3Fgd4kqqukkxbKnnJzQ">Lẫm lẫm tuế vân mộ - 凜凜歲云暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-S%C3%B9ng/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-Sxhd0GyVC7qZhAkCaf0d6g">Vương Chiêu Quân từ - 王昭君辭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-S%C3%B9ng/author-Vp0DUW6qXKB_-T0oNli1fg">Thạch Sùng</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
